{"tid":857592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲少年拒絕被人妻淫　慘遭鐵夾「火燒雞」","createTime":"2018-10-11T07:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T09:51:20.000Z","uid":122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c014b3f79c2c7f0929171e6e3114dc707f8dedd0","tid":857592,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181011/640_909f6a025d23e42dba5a82c46243df84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181011%2F640_909f6a025d23e42dba5a82c46243df84.jpg&h=940b4436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度再度發生性侵事件，但這次施暴者變成了女性。一名20多歲人妻欲求不滿，看上一名13歲少年，還想淫了人家。但少年拒絕人妻的要求，最後慘遭人妻拿燒燙的鐵夾夾下體，慘變「火燒雞」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，事發在新德里的「Chapraula」村莊，這名淫蕩人妻於周五下午，獨自引誘這名少年到她的家中，更企圖姦淫人家，但少年強力抗拒，人妻一怒之下，拿了燒燙的鐵夾，直接對少年的下體施以烙刑，導致少年的生殖器慘變「火燒雞」。之後少年的母親報警，母親也說，人妻已非第一次勾引她家乖兒子了，先前也有多次紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n目前這名人妻在逃，警方表示會進行全方位搜查與調查，並指控人妻涉及監禁、綁架、脅迫等罪。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"1031b46c2389f35f081860dccfeb77003b76d703","tid":857592,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"火燒雞雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2bccc5cccc6ac09d21c45a4c4d77304097d5fb","tid":857592,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"燒春雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6c3ea19971a837a1125cd7ff24319bb07a7d6e","tid":857592,"uid":154872,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快點強姦樓豬！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0212a42801d059f1d45d317466ece33ed0e90ad4","tid":857592,"